1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:08,500
In the year 2015 A.D., humanity was still recovering from the catastrophe known as "Second Impact."

2
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:15,000
Welcome to the special agency NERV, Shinji Ikari.

3
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:21,500
Target confirmed. Massive object detected approaching Tokyo-3.

4
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:28,000
An Angel, as I thought. The first one in fifteen years.

5
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:35,000
Conventional weapons from the UN forces have absolutely no effect against the Angel.

6
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:41,500
As long as it's deploying an AT Field, conventional weapons are powerless.

7
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:48,000
Commander Ikari, requesting authorization to use an N2 mine.

8
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:55,500
Activate Evangelion Unit-01. Has the pilot arrived?

9
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:02,500
I'm supposed to... ride this thing? This robot?

10
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:09,500
An Eva is not a robot. It is the multipurpose humanoid decisive weapon — the artificial human, Evangelion.

11
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:16,000
Get in. Otherwise, go home.

12
00:01:19,500 --> 00:01:23,000
Father... you called me here just for this?

13
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:29,500
The synchronization rate is abnormally high. These readings are unprecedented for an initial connection.

14
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:36,500
Eva Unit-01, launch preparations complete. Release all restraints.

15
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:43,500
Connected to launch catapult. Initiating launch sequence.

16
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:50,500
Evangelion Unit-01, launch!

17
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:57,500
The Angel is attacking! Take evasive action!

18
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:04,500
Unit-01 is out of control! The pilot's vital signs are dropping rapidly!

19
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:12,000
Unit-01 has... gone berserk? Is this the Eva's true form?

20
00:02:15,500 --> 00:02:19,000
Angel silence confirmed. Pattern blue, annihilated. Primary operation, complete.
